README = """
# RoofClaimPros CRM

RoofClaimPros CRM is a full-stack application built with **FastAPI (Backend)** and **React (Frontend)**.
It allows users to create accounts, verify email using OTP, login using OAuth providers, and manage purchased roofing leads.

------------------------------------------------------------

PROJECT OVERVIEW

This project provides:

• Email registration with OTP verification  
• Login using email and password  
• OAuth login with Google, Facebook, and Instagram  
• Lead management dashboard  
• Add / view / delete leads  

------------------------------------------------------------

SERVER INFORMATION

Backend Server

Framework: FastAPI  
Runs on: http://127.0.0.1:9000  

Command to run server:

uvicorn main:app --reload --port 9000


Frontend Server

Framework: React  
Runs on: http://localhost:3000  

Command to run frontend:

npm start

------------------------------------------------------------

API BASE URL

All backend APIs run under:

http://127.0.0.1:9000

------------------------------------------------------------

AUTHENTICATION ROUTES

POST /auth/login  
Login with email and password

POST /auth/register  
Create new user account

POST /auth/send-otp  
Send email OTP for verification

POST /auth/verify-otp  
Verify OTP sent to email

------------------------------------------------------------

OAUTH ROUTES

Google OAuth

GET /google/login
Starts Google OAuth login flow

GET /google/callback
Handles Google OAuth callback


Facebook OAuth

GET /facebook/login
Starts Facebook OAuth login flow

GET /facebook/callback
Handles Facebook OAuth callback


Instagram OAuth

GET /instagram/login
Starts Instagram OAuth login flow

GET /instagram/callback
Handles Instagram OAuth callback

------------------------------------------------------------

LEADS API

GET /leads
Fetch all leads

POST /leads
Create a new lead

DELETE /leads/{lead_index}
Delete a lead by index

------------------------------------------------------------

PROJECT STRUCTURE

Backend

backend/
│
├── main.py
├── auth/
│   ├── google_auth.py
│   ├── facebook_auth.py
│   ├── instagram_auth.py
│
├── routes/
│   └── leads.py
│
├── models/
│   └── lead_schema.py
│
└── .env


Frontend

frontend/
│
├── src/
│   ├── pages/
│   │   ├── Login.jsx
│   │   ├── CreateAccount.jsx
│   │   ├── VerifyEmail.jsx
│   │   └── Dashboard.jsx
│   │
│   ├── styles/
│   ├── assets/
│   └── App.js
│
└── .env

------------------------------------------------------------

ENVIRONMENT VARIABLES

Backend .env

GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID=
GOOGLE_CLIENT_SECRET=
GOOGLE_REDIRECT_URI=

FACEBOOK_CLIENT_ID=
FACEBOOK_CLIENT_SECRET=
FACEBOOK_REDIRECT_URI=

INSTAGRAM_CLIENT_ID=
INSTAGRAM_CLIENT_SECRET=
INSTAGRAM_REDIRECT_URI=

FRONTEND_BASE_URL=http://localhost:3000


Frontend .env

REACT_APP_API_BASE_URL=http://127.0.0.1:9000

------------------------------------------------------------

INSTALLATION

1 Clone the repository

git clone https://github.com/yourusername/roofclaimpros-crm.git

2 Install backend dependencies

cd backend
pip install -r requirements.txt

3 Run backend server

uvicorn main:app --reload --port 9000

4 Install frontend dependencies

cd frontend
npm install

5 Run frontend

npm start

------------------------------------------------------------

SECURITY FEATURES

• OAuth authentication  
• PKCE flow for Google OAuth  
• Email OTP verification  
• Environment variable configuration  
• No hardcoded credentials  

------------------------------------------------------------

FUTURE IMPROVEMENTS

• PostgreSQL database integration  
• JWT authentication  
• Role based access control  
• Docker deployment  
• Analytics dashboard  

------------------------------------------------------------

Author

RoofClaimPros Development Team
"""